room_title: Escape room "Shawshank v2" by Axxiom Escape Rooms Rehoboth in Rehoboth Beach
room_description: You will literally have to escape prison in order to achieve this Exodus. Based on a prison theme, there are very few distinct clues to aid you in your escape. Time will definitely work against you in this exodus. Only the quickest of thinkers will have a legitimate shot.
